<div id="pw_reset_request">
 <div class="form_header">
<h3 >W090-密码重置</h3>
</div>
<form class="show_form" action="/users/pw_sent_confirm">
  <div class="field">
    <label for="email">你的邮箱:</label>
    <input id="email" name="email" type="text" value="" />
  </div>
  <div class="actions">
    <input type="submit" class="submit_button_pw_reset " value="确认"  />
  </div>

  <p>
    <label class="error" style="margin-left:120px;"><%=flash[:notice]%></label>
  </p>
</form>

<div>点击确认后,请到你的Email邮箱接收邮件，点击密码重置链接，然后可重置密码</div>

</div>